      <div xml:id="Sonnet41"> 
              <interpGrp type="poembox">
                <interp ana="#form" type="Free"></interp>
                <interp ana="#tone" type="other"></interp>
                <interp ana="#topic" type="love"></interp>
              </interpGrp>
             <lg> 
               <l>I had a dream and in the dream i wove you a poem</l>
               <l>i used the fiber of my character to create spools of silken thread</l> 
               <l>dipped in the juices of my passion i dyed them in the colors of my imagination</l>
               <l>re-enforced each and every single strand with the strength of my love</l>
        
                 
                 
               
                 
                 
             
                 
                 
                 
                 
                
                 
              
                 
                 
                
  
               
               
               
